The possibilities are endless. You can make it human, super-human, or it doesn't even have to be a human. Determine if it is a male or female. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b7/Make-Supervillains-Step-1Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Make-Supervillains-Step-1Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/b/b7/Make-Supervillains-Step-1Bullet1.jpg/aid209724-v4-728px-Make-Supervillains-Step-1Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Try to stay away from bright colors. A cape is a good touch, but it's not necessary. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4f/Make-Supervillains-Step-1Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Make-Supervillains-Step-1Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/4/4f/Make-Supervillains-Step-1Bullet2.jpg/aid209724-v4-728px-Make-Supervillains-Step-1Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Make it either a creature or have them morph into a shape-shifter for extra effects. Shape-shifters are characters that go from a basic form, such as humans, to different creatures (like Maleficent in Sleeping Beauty). {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/3/38/Make-Supervillains-Step-1Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Make-Supervillains-Step-1Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/3/38/Make-Supervillains-Step-1Bullet3.jpg/aid209724-v4-728px-Make-Supervillains-Step-1Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
